Pre-Game Insights: Namibia hopes to keep up momentum as they seek to secure their maiden World Cup qualification.
Tunisia has gone through a spell of underwhelming performances, needing penalties to beat New Zealand when they played an international friendly in March.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Namibia made history as they made it to the knockout stage of the Africa Cup of Nations (Afcon) for the very first time earlier this year.
Others: The winners of the groups will qualify for the next World Cup finals, and the second-placed teams will enter a playoff round which will decide which two sides will get spots in the tournament.
